i> is the perpendicular distance between any two non-adjacent sides, which =
equals the diameter of the circle inscribed. The diagonals of lengths <i>p<=
/i> and <i>q</i> are the red dotted line segments.</figcaption></figure>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Diagonals">Diagonals</h2></=
div>
