-align: -2.005ex; width:13.719ex; height:5.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \l=
eft|{\frac {x}{a}}\right|\!+\left|{\frac {y}{b}}\right|\!=3D1.}"></span></d=
d></dl>
<p>The vertices are at <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inl=
ine"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"d=
isplay: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=
