xponent 1.
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Other_properties">Other pro=
perties</h2></div>
<ul><li>One of the five 2D <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lattice=
_(group)" title=3D"Lattice (group)">lattice</a> types is the rhombic lattic=
e, also called <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Centered_rectangula=
