<li>Rhombi can tile the 2D plane edge-to-edge and periodically in three dif=
ferent ways, including, for the 60=C2=B0 rhombus, the <a href=3D"https://en=
.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rhombille_tiling" title=3D"Rhombille tiling">rhombille =
tiling</a>.</li></ul>
